[{"type":"p","props":{"children":["This source plugin only supports fixed set of Plone REST API expansions, currently ",{"type":"em","props":{"children":["breadcrumbs"]}}," and ",{"type":"em","props":{"children":["navigation"]}},", which are both published as their own GraphQL nodes, ",{"type":"em","props":{"children":["PloneBreadcrumbs"]}}," and ",{"type":"em","props":{"children":["PloneNavigation"]}}," respectively."]}},{"type":"p","props":{"children":["Expansions are ",{"type":"a","props":{"href":"https://plonerestapi.readthedocs.io/en/latest/expansion.html","children":["plone.restapi"]}}," mechanism to embed additional “components”, such as ",{"type":"em","props":{"children":["navigation, breadcrumbs, schema,"]}}," or ",{"type":"em","props":{"children":["workflow"]}}," within the main content response, helping the API consumers to avoid unnecessary requests."]}},{"type":"p","props":{"children":["For instance, a normal GET request to ",{"type":"code","props":{"children":["http://localhost:8080/Plone"]}}," would give the following response:"]}},{"type":"pre","props":{"children":[{"type":"code","props":{"className":"language-json","children":["{
  "@components": {
    "actions": {
      "@id": "http://localhost:8080/Plone/@actions"
    },
    "breadcrumbs": {
      "@id": "http://localhost:8080/Plone/@breadcrumbs"
    },
    "navigation": {
      "@id": "http://localhost:8080/Plone/@navigation"
    }
  },
  "@id": "http://localhost:8080/Plone",
  "@type": "Plone Site",
  "id": "Plone",
  "...": "..."
}"]}}]}},{"type":"p","props":{"children":["But in the case we need the ",{"type":"em","props":{"children":["breadcrumbs, navigation"]}}," data or so on, we'll need to make more requests to ",{"type":"code","props":{"children":["/@breadcrumbs"]}},", ",{"type":"code","props":{"children":["/@navigation"]}}," and more depending on the data we need."]}},{"type":"p","props":{"children":["Expansions simplifies this process by retrieving all data in a single request as ",{"type":"code","props":{"children":["http://localhost:8080/Plone?expand=breadcrumbs,navigation"]}}," giving the response:"]}},{"type":"pre","props":{"children":[{"type":"code","props":{"className":"language-json","children":["{
  "@components": {
    "actions": {
      "@id": "http://localhost:8080/Plone/@actions"
    },
    "breadcrumbs": {
      "@id": "http://localhost:8080/Plone/@breadcrumbs",
      "items": []
    },
    "navigation": {
      "@id": "http://localhost:8080/Plone/@navigation",
      "items": [
        {
          "@id": "http://localhost:8080/Plone",
          "description": "",
          "title": "Home"
        },
        {
          "@id": "http://localhost:8080/Plone/news",
